            "title": "港股藥明系逆勢走強，藥明康得大升15%！「CXO一哥」邁入百億營收大關",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>Investing.com -</strong>周二，4月28日，港股三大指數集體調整，藥明系逆勢拉升，藥明康得 (HK:2359)大升15%，藥明合聯 (HK:2268)升超4%，藥明生物 (HK:2269)、藥明巨諾-B (HK:2126)升超2%.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">消息面上，「CXO一哥」藥明康得公告稱，2026年第一季度實現營業收入124.36億元，同比增長28.81%，首次在第一季度邁入百億大關；歸屬于上市公司股東的淨利潤為46.52億元，同比增長26.68%。截至今年一季度末，藥明康得持續經營業務在手訂單總額高達597.7億元，同比增長23.6%。</p><blockquote class=\"border-pebble mx-5 my-7.5 border-l-2 pl-5 italic\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-dolphin\"><strong><u><span>財報季，美股數字睇到眼花？</span></u></strong> <strong><u><span>Warren AI</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>一鍵解讀數據！現在</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>InvestingPro</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>立享</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>50%</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>折扣，</span></u></strong> <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"即刻點擊訂閱\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:即刻點擊訂閱;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.investing.com/pro/pricing?utm_medium=feed&amp;utm_source=yahoo&amp;utm_campaign=yahoo-hk\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><strong><em><span>即刻點擊訂閱</span></em></strong></a><strong><u><span>！</span></u></strong></p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/4Rs4q5xaqbbQ1veFYL1cPw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://d55-invdn-com.investing.com/content/4eec8a5b6f70fa27a6a6e919476ddff5.png\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-dolphin\"><span><br/></span></p></blockquote></div>",
